1.1.name: wordpress/bmlt-tabbed-ui
1.1.description: This plugin provides a jQuery Tabbed UI for the Basic Meeting List Toolbox (BMLT). You must have BMLT installed and running. Simply put the shortcode into a Wordpress page to get your very own tabbed interface to BMLT. Not into a tabbed interface? There is a template for displaying meetings in a table without tabs. This plugin also provides various shortcodes to return the number of meetings and groups in specified service bodies. Please visit settings - BMLT Tabbed UI for shortcode instructions.
